  <h2>Data handling</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>On-premise isolation; TLS at the edge; no public model access.</li>
    <li>PII redaction in logs (names/phones/emails).</li>
    <li>Scoped, read-only adapters to CRM/DMS in Phase-1.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Prompt & model controls</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>System/meta prompts; persona scoping per department.</li>
    <li>Uncertainty handling (“I’m not sure … here’s what I can do”).</li>
    <li>Offline test harness; regression checks; changelog.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Governance</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>PR-based change; approvers by role; audit trail.</li>
    <li>Release notes; playbook updates; training refresh cadence.</li>
  </ul>

